Body:
assert ee('1') == '1'
assert ee('1.0') == '1.0'
assert ee('a') == 'a'
assert ee('[a]') == ['a']
assert ee('(a)') == ('a',)
assert ee('(a, , )') == ('a',)
assert ee('[a, , ]') == ['a']
assert ee('true') == True
assert ee('[true]') == [True]
assert ee('[true, false]') == [True, False]
assert ee('(true, false)') == (True, False)
